{"tid":5404,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Angelababy曝兒時萌照 「從小美到大」破整形傳言","createTime":"2016-11-27T00:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T05:33:58.000Z","uid":17919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9d503cc85d5f3c0fb1628bdfe50d8ad5360661","tid":5404,"uid":17919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"Angelababy曝兒時萌照 「從小美到大」破整形傳言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K011hw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK011hw.jpg&h=0a2d7539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕「Angelababy」楊穎與黃曉明結婚1年，做人成功，自宣布懷孕消息以來，令粉絲又驚又喜，相當期待baby的出生，她今日在IG分享兒時照，更讓粉絲大嘆：「從小美到大！」<br />\nAngelababy目前已懷有5個月身孕，樂當稱職人妻，今日在IG開心的大曬兒時嫩照，讓大批粉絲看的大呼「超级可爱」，照片中，Angelababy綁著2束馬尾，稚嫩的臉蛋相當可愛，比起一旁同年的小朋友，個頭來的高出許多，有愛的牽著一旁的妹妹，模樣相當萌，讓不少粉絲看了直誇「從小美到大」、「真的從小就好看」，更有粉絲大呼「破了整容輿論」，表示Angelababy自曝兒時照，根本間接破先前整形一說，大力挺偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">睇下召唔召喚到</span></span>"},{"pid":"762fd3d94dce9b01657a0c3d11453c2ddfa279a7","tid":5404,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:57:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span>"},{"pid":"8477ebdefc0bc3f98fd42bdab6bcf96785e5bfe8","tid":5404,"uid":3094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">的</span>"},{"pid":"6d787fa4260f5244042d382260d975c7784d64fb","tid":5404,"uid":23938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">的</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樣</span>"},{"pid":"b43e7a3c9074a98ae43f82907f28ccb6f2581ea0","tid":5404,"uid":426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re